      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why im still typing this. everything just feels so heavy. the lab results came back again and it's just... another dead end. the funding is drying up and my advisor basically stopped looking me in the eye weeks ago. i feel like i've spent my whole life building this one thing and now it's just gone. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fix things that are fundamentally broken.",
